{"tid":1675714,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點先可以信翻條仔？","createTime":"2019-10-26T05:31:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T10:20:00.000Z","uid":305822,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1019405b102241308ab459236452a537134914fb","tid":1675714,"uid":305822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T05:31:38.000Z","msg":"［代Po]<br />\n話說依幾排我覺得我條仔好古怪<br />\n有次我想借佢電話用 因為冇曬數據 <br />\n點知佢唔肯即刻比我 佢去完個廁所先比我<br />\n咁我就覺得有啲唔對路 就去問佢嘅兄弟知唔知咩事<br />\n點知佢兄弟同我講原來佢我條仔一直都有玩類似Tinder嘅交友apps <br />\n仲有原來我條仔瞞過我 自己同朋友去飲野 仲係bar定唔知club識咗一條女 之後仲同佢兄弟講條女好正<br />\n咁我一直都好信我男朋友嘅 所以尋晚就問清楚佢<br />\n佢一開頭都話冇嘅 咁我同佢講我有朋友影到佢去飲野嘅相<br />\n佢先話有暪我飲野 但死都唔認有掂女<br />\n我條仔叫我信佢 但我一諗起佢同條女唔知做啲咩<br />\n我個人打哂冷震 <br />\n依家完全唔想見佢 我好想信佢 但我唔識<br />\n有冇人可以教下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8667f757b7cb03bdabd1c16c83f4e2feffff0ac","tid":1675714,"uid":179837,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T05:32:59.000Z","msg":"唔用信 只要分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48a73d02f2768df845c794da22a46b676a62d9b9","tid":1675714,"uid":181997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T05:38:33.000Z","msg":"勿信只分"},{"pid":"a1adfd665b159d1d15abb27e444a62ab77998cd4","tid":1675714,"uid":253773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T05:39:08.000Z","msg":"一係而家分搵下個啱你又對你專一嘅人，一係下個搵毒撚埋單，因為唔會有decent嘅人會幫人埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"098c6aa5a3b5f1ab62a9ca6f47b2280fdbdcab6c","tid":1675714,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T05:41:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q4tpW01.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ4tpW01.gif&h=a4587eba&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rG9c5Um.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrG9c5Um.gif&h=4ad4d108&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40766b11c23902f8b4fc97bc059115cbd3fd2c44","tid":1675714,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T05:56:11.000Z","msg":"信就信，分就分<br />\n如果要搵方法逼自己信，咁不如分，或者接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"796b4cef33d437f5b00d9d98139bc55c79bfd9a3","tid":1675714,"uid":15957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T06:11:24.000Z","msg":"佢兄弟都唔係咩好人"},{"pid":"44b56693f72e7324856f743a027d38734288c9d7","tid":1675714,"uid":305822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"796b4cef33d437f5b00d9d98139bc55c79bfd9a3","tid":1675714,"uid":15957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T06:11:24.000Z","msg":"佢兄弟都唔係咩好人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T07:09:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62d8bd521347df371b07eaef9ba8400a0fd22a12","tid":1675714,"uid":75889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T09:21:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9c76641940d2506fd78fe542ce5c3e4a41a0633","tid":1675714,"uid":305822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62d8bd521347df371b07eaef9ba8400a0fd22a12","tid":1675714,"uid":75889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T09:21:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T09:30:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ae74d86bcb81067e056d1f77e95c4978b278ebf","tid":1675714,"uid":319969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T10:20:00.000Z","msg":"其實真係要分手<br />\n佢個心已經唔喺度<br />\n係點留都唔會留得住<br />\n<br />\n係要冷靜翻個人<br />\n同自己講<br />\n要離開佢<br />\n識過一個<br />\n<br />\n我知呢件事好難<br />\n我自己都未必做到<br />\n但真係要絕情一啲<br />\n唔好再喺佢身上浪費時間<br />\n<br />\n偷食唔認最撚仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}